# Beamcore Environment Variables
#
# Beamcore reads provider API keys from the environment. You can also
# configure providers interactively with `/api add` inside the TUI.
#
# Set the variables for your provider(s) below. Uncomment the ones you need.

# OpenAI
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Anthropic (Claude)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Mistral
# MISTRAL_API_KEY=...

# Any OpenAI-compatible provider (Groq, Together, OpenRouter, etc.)
# Set the base URL and API key:
# OPENAI_API_BASE=https://api.groq.com/openai
# OPENAI_API_KEY=gsk_...
